path = datapath(path)
(QH, s_freq_cutoff, h_freq_cutoff, freq_scale_factor, temp, solv, spc,
    invert, d3) = False, 100.0, 100.0, 1.0, 298.15, 'none', False, False, 0
if conc == False:
    conc = GV.ATMOS / (GV.GAS_CONSTANT * temp)
bbe = GV.calc_bbe(path, QS, QH, s_freq_cutoff, h_freq_cutoff, temp, conc,
    freq_scale_factor, solv, spc, invert, d3)
precision = 6
assert E == round(bbe.scf_energy, precision)
if hasattr(bbe, 'gibbs_free_energy'):
    assert ZPE == round(bbe.zpe, precision)
    assert H == round(bbe.enthalpy, precision)
    assert TS == round(temp * bbe.entropy, precision)
    assert TqhS == round(temp * bbe.qh_entropy, precision)
    assert G == round(bbe.gibbs_free_energy, precision)
    assert qhG == round(bbe.qh_gibbs_free_energy, precision)
pytest.mark.parametrize('path, conc, QS, E, ZPE, H, TS, TqhS, G, qhG', [(
    'media_conc/Benzene.log', 0, 'grimme', -232.227201, 0.101377, -

    0.021627, 0.021627, -75.31906, -75.31906), ('media_conc/MeOH.log', 0,

    232.153263), ('media_conc/H2O.log', 0, 'truhlar', -75.322774, 0.021564,
    -75.297433, 0.021627, 0.021627, -75.31906, -75.31906), (
    'media_conc/MeOH.log', 0, 'truhlar', -114.17905, 0.054749, -114.120139,
    0.026909, 0.026909, -114.147048, -114.147048), (
